{"info": {"author": "George P. <digitalduke@gmail.com>, Dmitry Krukov <glebov.ru@gmail.com>", "author_email": "digitalduke@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules"], "description": "amoCRM python API wrapper \n-------------------------\n\npython [amoCRM](https://www.amocrm.ru/) API wrapper with a human interface for easy use\n\nforked from [amocrm_api](https://github.com/Krukov/amocrm_api)  \n\n\nInstallation\n============\n\n```\npip install amoapi\n```\n\n\nUsage\n=====\n\n\nThere are 7 abstraction of 5 AmoCRM objects:\n\n- \u041a\u043e\u043d\u0442\u0430\u043a\u0442 - BaseContact\n- \u041a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f  - BaseCompany\n- \u0421\u0434\u0435\u043b\u043a\u0430 - BaseLead\n- \u0417\u0430\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0430 - (LeadTask, ContactTask)\n- \u0421\u043e\u0431\u044b\u0442\u0438\u0435 - (LeadNote, ContactNote)\n\nSettings\n--------\n\nFirst of all you need to define settings:\n\n```python\nfrom amocrm import BaseContact, amo_settings, fields\namo_settings.set('krukov@centrobit.ru', '4b332718c4c5944003af7e6389860ced', 'testcentrobit')\n```\n\n\nCustom field\n------------\n\nOne of the features of AmoCRM in the presence of custom fields in a contact, company and lead objects\n\nTo define your custom field you need describe it:\n\n```python\nfrom amocrm import BaseContact, amo_settings, fields\n\namo_settings.set('<put user email here>', '<put user_hash here>', '<put domain here>')\n\nclass Contact(BaseContact):\n    position = fields.CustomField(u'\u0414\u043e\u043b\u0436\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c')\n    site = fields.CustomField(u'\u0421\u0430\u0439\u0442')\n    phone = fields.EnumCustomField(u'\u0422\u0435\u043b\u0435\u0444\u043e\u043d', enum='WORK')\n```\n\nOk, now it is ready to use and you can get, create or edit contacts:\n\n```python\nnew_contact = Contact(name='Example2', company='ExampleCorp2', position='QA', phone='0001')\nnew_contact.site = 'http://example.com'\nnew_contact.save()\n\ncontact = Contact.objects.get(new_contact.id)\ncontact_search = Contact.objects.search('Example2')\nassert contact.id == contact_search.id\nprint(contact.phone)\ncontact.phone = '8-800-00000000'\ncontact.save()\ncontact.create_task('New task, yeee', task_type=u'\u0417\u0432\u043e\u043d\u043e\u043a',\n                 complete_till=datetime.datetime.now()+datetime.timedelta(days=3))\nprint(contact.notes)\nprint(contact.tasks)\n```", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/digitalduke/amoapi", "keywords": "", "license": "MIT license", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "amoapi", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/amoapi/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/amoapi/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/digitalduke/amoapi"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/amoapi/0.9.1/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "python API wrapper for amoCRM", "version": "0.9.1", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h2>amoCRM python API wrapper</h2>\n<p>python <a href=\"https://www.amocrm.ru/\" rel=\"nofollow\">amoCRM</a> API wrapper with a human interface for easy use</p>\n<p>forked from <a href=\"https://github.com/Krukov/amocrm_api\" rel=\"nofollow\">amocrm_api</a></p>\n<h1>Installation</h1>\n<pre><code>pip install amoapi\n</code></pre>\n<h1>Usage</h1>\n<p>There are 7 abstraction of 5 AmoCRM objects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u041a\u043e\u043d\u0442\u0430\u043a\u0442 - BaseContact</li>\n<li>\u041a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f  - BaseCompany</li>\n<li>\u0421\u0434\u0435\u043b\u043a\u0430 - BaseLead</li>\n<li>\u0417\u0430\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0430 - (LeadTask, ContactTask)</li>\n<li>\u0421\u043e\u0431\u044b\u0442\u0438\u0435 - (LeadNote, ContactNote)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Settings</h2>\n<p>First of all you need to define settings:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">amocrm</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">BaseContact</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">amo_settings</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">fields</span>\n<span class=\"n\">amo_settings</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">set</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'krukov@centrobit.ru'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'4b332718c4c5944003af7e6389860ced'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'testcentrobit'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<h2>Custom field</h2>\n<p>One of the features of AmoCRM in the presence of custom fields in a contact, company and lead objects</p>\n<p>To define your custom field you need describe it:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">amocrm</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">BaseContact</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">amo_settings</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">fields</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">amo_settings</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">set</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'&lt;put user email here&gt;'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'&lt;put user_hash here&gt;'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'&lt;put domain here&gt;'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">Contact</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">BaseContact</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">position</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">fields</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">CustomField</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"sa\">u</span><span class=\"s1\">'\u0414\u043e\u043b\u0436\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">site</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">fields</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">CustomField</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"sa\">u</span><span class=\"s1\">'\u0421\u0430\u0439\u0442'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">phone</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">fields</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">EnumCustomField</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"sa\">u</span><span class=\"s1\">'\u0422\u0435\u043b\u0435\u0444\u043e\u043d'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">enum</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'WORK'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Ok, now it is ready to use and you can get, create or edit contacts:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">new_contact</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Contact</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Example2'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">company</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'ExampleCorp2'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">position</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'QA'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">phone</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'0001'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">new_contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">site</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'http://example.com'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">new_contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">save</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">contact</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">objects</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">new_contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">contact_search</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">objects</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">search</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'Example2'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">assert</span> <span class=\"n\">contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">id</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">contact_search</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">id</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">phone</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">phone</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'8-800-00000000'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">save</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"n\">contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create_task</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'New task, yeee'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">task_type</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"sa\">u</span><span class=\"s1\">'\u0417\u0432\u043e\u043d\u043e\u043a'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                 <span class=\"n\">complete_till</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">datetime</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">datetime</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">now</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"n\">datetime</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">timedelta</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">days</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">notes</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">contact</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tasks</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 7119054, "releases": {"0.9.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "c6192a9f43499cb2b104e46eaf9936af", "sha256": "9996bdcb58c2fa7aef3b734dc33bca5037e4dffca4bc5fd8ceb827682210ff72"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "amoapi-0.9.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "c6192a9f43499cb2b104e46eaf9936af", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 16916, "upload_time": "2020-04-14T09:26:25", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-14T09:26:25.166749Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/af/ce/f43418d79a7aa04900a42f7094b7e5c907ae238bae38975e28b856e854c0/amoapi-0.9.0.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.9.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "21e178af2336ba0695ba668dbf549ad5", "sha256": "61ef7ac9bd51d6e89dac37a33c75603c05cd08ea4fe4fef4c8d86185220acec5"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "amoapi-0.9.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "21e178af2336ba0695ba668dbf549ad5", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 16974, "upload_time": "2020-04-28T10:41:32", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-28T10:41:32.621465Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/d5/21/06275992e166d1d51f6f2f72ae05ea0601eeb499a31075c40fe2eace2bee/amoapi-0.9.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}]}, "urls": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "21e178af2336ba0695ba668dbf549ad5", "sha256": "61ef7ac9bd51d6e89dac37a33c75603c05cd08ea4fe4fef4c8d86185220acec5"}, "downl